<body bgcolor="#ffffff">
<HR ALIGN="center" SIZE="1">
<font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="-1"> 
<h3><center>THE MASKS FOR THEMES/CATEGORIES</center></h3>
<h4><center><a href="themes.html.de">deutsche version</a></center></h4>
<HR ALIGN="center" SIZE="1">
<OL>
	<LI>&nbsp;<STRONG>name</STRONG>:&nbsp;The name of the category, e.g. 'Residenzpflicht'.
	<BR><BR>
	<LI>&nbsp;<STRONG>beschreibung</STRONG>:&nbsp;A short description of the category for internal use.
	<BR><BR>
	<LI>&nbsp;<STRONG>filename</STRONG>:&nbsp;the filename of the category. Please use only small letters, e.g. 'residenzpflicht'.
	<BR><BR>
	<LI>&nbsp;<STRONG>hauptinfoseite</STRONG>:&nbsp;An external www-site which contains more on this category may be announced here. This reference is being produced into the head of the themesite.
	<BR><BR>
	</OL>

</body>
</html>